{
  "text": "Other existing approaches Midi [CITATION_1] , Charm-L [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] in addition to computing redescriptions which has time complexity larger than O((|V 1 | + |V 2 ) \u00b7 |E||), require discretization of continuous attributes which has a time complexity of O(|E| \u00b7 log(|E|) \u00b7 (|V 1 | + |V 2 |)) if equal width or equal frequency approach is used. However, this needs to be performed only once.",
